    'subscribe.faq.title': 'Frequently Asked Questions',
    'subscribe.faq.q1': 'What are credits?',
    'subscribe.faq.a1': 'Credits are the currency used to process images on our platform. Each watermark removal operation consumes 1 credit. You can earn credits by subscribing to our plans or through special promotions.',
    'subscribe.faq.q2': 'Do I need to register to use RemoveWatermark to remove watermarks?',
    'subscribe.faq.a2': 'Yes, registration is required to use our service. This allows us to track your credits, save your processing history, and provide you with a better user experience.',
    'subscribe.faq.q3': 'Is RemoveWatermark free?',
    'subscribe.faq.a3': 'New users receive 5 free credits upon registration. After using these free credits, you can subscribe to one of our affordable plans to continue using the service.',
    'subscribe.faq.q4': 'Should I choose pay-as-you-go credits or a subscription plan?',
    'subscribe.faq.a4': 'Subscription plans offer better value with more credits per dollar. If you need to process images regularly, a subscription plan is recommended. Pay-as-you-go credits are ideal for occasional users.',
    'subscribe.faq.q5': 'What if I\'m not satisfied with the results?',
    'subscribe.faq.a5': 'We strive to provide high-quality results. If you\'re not satisfied, please contact our support team at support@chdaoai.com and we\'ll do our best to help you. However, credits used for processing cannot be refunded.',
    'subscribe.faq.q6': 'What if I run out of credit limit?',
    'subscribe.faq.a6': 'If you run out of credits, you can purchase additional credits or upgrade to a higher subscription plan. You can also wait for your monthly credits to reset if you\'re on a subscription plan.',
    'subscribe.faq.q7': 'How much does it cost for additional usage beyond my monthly credits?',
    'subscribe.faq.a7': 'Additional credits beyond your monthly subscription can be purchased separately. Please contact our support team for pricing information on additional credit packages.',
    'subscribe.faq.q8': 'Is registration required before using RemoveWatermark?',
    'subscribe.faq.a8': 'Yes, registration is required. This helps us provide you with free credits, track your usage, and ensure a secure and personalized experience.',
    'subscribe.faq.q9': 'How many conversions can I perform using RemoveWatermark?',
    'subscribe.faq.a9': 'The number of conversions depends on your subscription plan. Basic plan includes 30 credits/month, Standard plan includes 100 credits/month, and Premium plan includes 350 credits/month. Each conversion uses 1 credit.',
    'subscribe.faq.q10': 'What are the accepted payment methods?',
    'subscribe.faq.a10': 'We accept various payment methods through our secure payment processor, including major credit cards, debit cards, and other online payment options.',
    'subscribe.faq.q11': 'Do you accept custom requests or specific needs?',
    'subscribe.faq.a11': 'For custom requests or bulk processing needs, please contact our support team at support@chdaoai.com. We\'ll be happy to discuss custom solutions that meet your specific requirements.',
    'subscribe.faq.q12': 'What if I want to perform a specific image conversion?',
    'subscribe.faq.a12': 'Our service focuses on watermark and logo removal. If you have specific conversion needs beyond watermark removal, please contact us at support@chdaoai.com to discuss your requirements.',
    'subscribe.faq.q13': 'What happens if I don\'t use the full amount of monthly credits?',
    'subscribe.faq.a13': 'Unused credits from your monthly subscription do not roll over to the next month. Each month, your credit balance resets to the amount included in your subscription plan. We recommend using your credits within the billing period.',
    'subscribe.faq.q14': 'Can I upgrade/downgrade/cancel my subscription?',
    'subscribe.faq.a14': 'Yes, you can upgrade, downgrade, or cancel your subscription at any time through your account settings. Changes to your plan will take effect at the start of the next billing cycle. Cancellation will prevent auto-renewal but your service will remain active until the end of the current billing period.',
    'subscribe.credits.title': 'How Credits Work',
    'subscribe.credits.what.title': 'What are credits?',
    'subscribe.credits.what.desc': 'Credits are the currency used to process images on our platform. Each image processing operation consumes credits based on the complexity of the task.',
    'subscribe.credits.usage.title': 'How are credits used?',
    'subscribe.credits.usage.desc': 'Each watermark removal or AI processing task uses 1-5 credits depending on the image size and complexity. Higher quality output requires more credits.',
    'subscribe.credits.unused.title': 'What happens to unused credits?',
    'subscribe.credits.unused.desc': 'Unused credits from your monthly subscription will expire at the end of each billing cycle and do not roll over to the next month.',
    'subscribe.credits.purchase.title': 'Can I purchase additional credits?',
    'subscribe.credits.purchase.desc': 'Yes, you can purchase additional credits at any time. Visit your profile page or contact support for more information on credit packages.',
